      * Structure to hold data for custom memory management.
      * pcre2-memctl.
           05 FILLER.
      * void *    (*malloc)(size_t, void *);
              10 FILLER             USAGE POINTER.
      * void      (*free)(void *, void *);
              10 FILLER             USAGE POINTER.
      * void      *memory_data;
              10 FILLER             USAGE POINTER.
